      <title>岸田继续日本对日元过度波动的警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/kishida-pledges-appropriate-action-against-excessive-yen-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄对日元贬值发出警告，并承诺在不排除任何选择的情况下对过度波动采取适当行动，继续针对日元大幅波动进行口头辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/kishida-pledges-appropriate-action-against-excessive-yen-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 07:05:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
